{"tid":657451,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"講吓你鍾意嘅煮食youtuber, 一齊討論下煮西餐","createTime":"2018-05-08T06:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T03:40:28.000Z","uid":91442,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c2fd73f8c5808e9a8f30e05592064e4c0e901a","tid":657451,"uid":91442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:25:02.000Z","msg":"Gennaro 呢個意大利大叔超好笑, 動作好誇張, 煮嘅意大利嘢亦都好簡單, 跟佢D片整個pizza, 都幾好食<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/gennarocontaldo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fgennarocontaldo&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=84fff58d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/gennarocontaldo</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個鍾意嘅係教煮西班牙菜嘅Albert, 暫時只係跟佢整過蒜蓉辣蝦, 不過其它佢嘅片睇落亦好易 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRmRqmB5uzpx7wWYEVVdCNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCRmRqmB5uzpx7wWYEVVdCNw&d=UO09%2BoZJNK498c%2Bwp3OlmP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c93a6fb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRmRqmB5uzpx7wWYEVVdCNw</a><br />\n<br />\n利申先, 無收過佢地錢<br />\n<br />\n當然本地高汁嘅有bob 叔, 最近跟佢整fujitas, 都幾好食<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲一齊討論下煮嘢食嘅片, 例如work 唔work, D 材料買完會唔會好嘥, etc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67233a18b78bd9612af882217c82537f3e5fb887","tid":657451,"uid":2741,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:26:50.000Z","msg":"epic meal time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a703073892c73cd488982b5236853f9be932774","tid":657451,"uid":26332,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:30:36.000Z","msg":"Gennaro 係 Jamie Oliver師父<br />\n好鐘意佢啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\